ygData.messageBody:
KNN, do you have to specially mentioned my name? ;)

Hey, not only me lah, Kellendil, Massiah etc all not yet lvl 50 wat.
Somemore I stop EQ for almost 6 mths, can excuse mah. Come back all old
birds busy killing naggy and planes hunting, bo lang PL me much, except Les
and Bibi PL me one session each so far, hehe, oh and Mass who train with me
at WK Barbie village
.
Anyway, seem like for same lvl, necro can solo lvl much better than wiz.
I've been training at Ulir and Ein with this DE Nec often, he always like
to brag abt how his necro can kill Ein with much lesser than wiz (he got a
lvl 50 wiz). Coz he always use snare, fear, dot, send pet and life tap.
Also keep bragging he can pass mana to others, can heal others (life tap),
his lvl 49 Dot inflict 1200 dam vs wiz's ice comet, and he can med while
his pet handle mobs blah blah blah...but wat to do? I'm so low lvl, no one
support (he lvl 42 now), so must act weakling lor, else he KS from me, how?
;) One thing, the fact that Necro can't travel like wiz and dru put me off
- I really hate to run.

Hey I say u old birds, shld organize some PL sessions for our non lvl 50
members lah. If we all achieve lvl 50, whole guild can go planes hunting
and dun need others' help liao, right?





On Sunday, 02 April, 2000 3:31 AM, Gary Qui Hong Loong
[SMTP:kanglun@...] wrote:
> Duno how many of the old bird still reading this list. Most of us in

Hate and just broke into Sky. Also killed Naggy on 5th try heheh. our guild
website is www.warquest.com/adv all is welcome to visit the page. Cheers.
